<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.10.2">
<l>ānirai mēyttaṉ ṟalaikaṭa laṭaittiṭ ṭarakkartañ ciraṅkaḷai yuruṭṭi</l>
<l>kārniṟai  mēkaṅ kalantatō ruruvak kaṇṇaṉār karutiya kōyil</l>
<l>pūniraic cerunti puṉṉaimut tarumpip potumpiṭai varivaṇṭu miṇṭi</l>
<l>tēṉirait tuṇṭaṅ kiṉṉicai muralun tiruveḷḷi yaṅkuṭi yatuvē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The temple where Kaṇṇaṉ appeared, his form [like] a gathering</l>
<l rend="indent">of rain-filled clouds,</l>
<l>Having grazed the cow herds, then dammed up the crashing sea,</l>
<l rend="indent">and rolled down the heads of the demon,</l>
<l>Is that very one - Tiruveḷḷiyaṅkuṭi where the sweet music of striped bees,</l>
<l rend="indent">buzzing and sipping nectar, resounds there,</l>
<l>Swarming inside hollows of laurel where sprout pearl[-like buds]</l>
<l rend="indent">and pear [trees] with rows of flowers.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
